      • checkGlobalFlags

        public boolean checkGlobalFlags(org.telegram.telegrambots.api.objects.Update update)
        Description copied from class: AbilityBot
        Test the update against the provided global flags. The default implementation requires a Flag.MESSAGE.

        This method should be overridden if the user wants updates that don't require a MESSAGE to pass through.

        Overrides:
        checkGlobalFlags in class AbilityBot
        Parameters:
        update - a Telegram Update
        Returns:
        true if the update satisfies the global flags
